snippet.textDisplay:
All I want to say that I lost my mother 3 years back. She was an inspiration, the whole circle of life and I have grown up watching her humming this song when I used to come back from school. Farida Khanum jee you have took me back to the past and i felt her presence so strongly at the moment while listening and watching you. I believe myself to be very strong, I am 30 but I have never cried like today since the day she died. There is nothing in this world that could ever bring her back but you made me believe that mothers never die, they will always be with you, they will always pray for you and watch your back. I want to touch your feets and pay my humble love in your regard..

May Allah bless you with health and wellness.

Jawad Jeral
Love from UAE :'(
